      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still bothering to wake up every morning. the last three years of my phd... the labs, the funding, the constant pressure... it's all just gone. i feel like i've spent my entire life building a person who doesn't actually exist anymore. i'm just so tired of fighting to keep my head above water when there's nothing left to save.",
